tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE VisualizationData (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  data_name VARCHAR(255),
  data_value FLOAT,
  visualization_type VARCHAR(50),
  date_inserted TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE VisualizationData (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  data_type VARCHAR(50),
  data_value DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE AggregationFunctions (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  function_name VARCHAR(50),
  function_description TEXT,
  function_example VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE DataSources (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  source_name VARCHAR(50),
  source_description TEXT,
  source_type VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE SummaryData (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  summary_type VARCHAR(50),
  summary_value DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE VisualizationTypes (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  type_name VARCHAR(50),
  type_description TEXT
)
